The paper deals with image inpainting using deep neural networks, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of stacked networks and residual polishing also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves image processing (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR) as it deals with repairing and modifying images.
